Package: prettypublisher
Type: Package
Version: 0.2.1.9000
Title: Formatting Functions for Publishable R Markdown Documents
Authors@R: c(person("Sam Abbott", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "contact@samabbott.co.uk"))
Description: Provides a variety of general purpose functions that help in formatting R markdown documents ready for publication. Specifically focussed on improving the appearance of word documents, although all functions should also work for both pdf, and html. 
